- **Build error TS6133 `zoom` unused**: After removing zoom-based colWidth in KanbanTimeline (changed to `Math.round(totalWidth / months.length)`), the `zoom` parameter remained in the function signature but was never used. TypeScript strict mode treats this as an error.
